data.text: 2013 Provider Directory Medica Clear Solution SM (PPO) Greater Minnesota, North Dakota and South Dakota Service Area This directory provides a list of Medica Clear Solution’s network providers. This directory is for select Minnesota, North Dakota and South Dakota counties. Please refer to the introduction pages for a listing of the counties in the service area. This directory is current as of 08/28/2012. Some network providers may have been added or removed from our network after this directory was printed. We do not guarantee that each provider is still accepting new members. To get the most up-to-date information about Medica Clear Solution’s network providers in your area, you can visit www.medica.com or call our Customer Service Department at 1-800-234-8755 or 952-992-2300, 8 a.m. to 8 p.m. Central Time, seven days a week. TTY users should call the National Relay Center at 1-800-855-2880. Medica is a health plan with a Medicare contract. Y0088_3192 CMS Accepted
